fields.name: Height
fields.description: The height of the rectangular region in pixels. This can be absolute pixel value (e.g 100), or relative to the size of the video (For example, 50%).

fields.name: Left
fields.description: The number of pixels from the left-margin. This can be absolute pixel value (e.g 100), or relative to the size of the video (For example, 50%).

fields.name: Top
fields.description: The number of pixels from the top-margin. This can be absolute pixel value (e.g 100), or relative to the size of the video (For example, 50%).

fields.name: Width
fields.description: The width of the rectangular region in pixels. This can be absolute pixel value (e.g 100), or relative to the size of the video (For example, 50%).
